info.name: MOCBOT API
info.description:
This document outlines the specifications behind the MOCBOT API

Some useful links:
- The [MOCBOT API](https://github.com/MasterOfCubesAU/mocbot-api) repository

Contact Support:
 Email: masterofcubesau@gmail.com
